"name":"Note: Normalize Lead Payload"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: mql, sql + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'mql' → HubSpot · ②→ Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"76685785-ffcc-e69e-e7fc-2d36fbf5cf8a","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Process 'mql' → HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"3dbcaa01-cc1b-c8f7-75f5-934cf3efa07d","name":"Note: Process 'mql' → HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert\n\ndiscord — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Discord webhook URL","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"e5131f95-cb26-a233-7854-f65fd0a8c82e","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Routed Work · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"42bdc18b-a7f2-112c-d93e-ca4501d9b3d1","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"25489b14-262a-85a3-19b5-f6cfe72d407d","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"4c32cd37-484b-73a6-d9ff-e45684e31ba1","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty email","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"148843e4-cea5-8573-bd08-a5bcd0cb83c2","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty email\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"bfd0a332-965f-23ed-bec2-9af1739f861e","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"2cd9e7c4-22b9-c45a-99b2-e0ab5ceee5c3","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"41bae7d9-952c-4187-3d1f-a8e6ea413bec","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"81ea02b4-3b46-28eb-9b08-41be7c1fb20f","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"5bc59b09-57c4-cb03-5483-e26cdbc1b97f","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"10b365ff-108d-c949-fd42-aa30c99e5071","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,1540],"id":"94967de4-0f5e-d52a-08ff-aa5b026feb20","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,1540],"id":"19c0b7af-3489-66d9-2351-bc2b1ff7291a","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Route inbound leads with HubSpot and Discord 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nRoute inbound leads with HubSpot and Discord 24/7. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual capture forms is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Normalize Lead Payload → Route by Work Type → Process 'mql' → HubSpot → Merge Routed Work → Cap Batch Volume → Tag Pipeline Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating capture forms in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Discord webhook URL; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"9d59b73d-cd3b-086f-1c68-0dd8e6e1f52f","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"20bf1354-5a94-856d-4f8a-72e2f62e3390","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your capture forms process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"fa6529b1-3b19-580e-4515-52de1e6a009e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Lead Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Lead Payload","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Lead Payload":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'mql' → HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'mql' → HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'sql' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty email":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"48550196-01f2-410a-96ee-f0087e2f4429","id":"FDX04149"}